TestNg--- Unit testing framework

purpose-- design test cases in systematic way, available in form of jar file

Java unit testing framework
Generated good HTML reports
Gives lot of annotations
define sequence, priorities of test cases
Dependency feature (1 tc dependent on other)
Grouping of testing


Imp--- Data provider 
(Ex: used for login of 10 different users...)
TestNg is also called as TDD framework (test driven development)--- along with development testing is carried out


Install Testng in eclipse
url-- http://beust.com/eclipse/



1. Data Drive: from different resources
a. Excel file--- test data
b. Properties file---  env variables, OR, test data
c. testng.xml---- env variables
d. DB
e. XMl file
f. JSON file